**algorithm**
- Base Case: `if (n === 0)  return 1;`
- Recurrence Relation: `N**N = N**(N/2 x 2) = N**(N/2) x N**(N/2)`

**complexity**
- Time Complexity: O(log2 N)
- Space Complexity: O(log2 N)
```JavaScript
/**
 * @param {number} x
 * @param {number} n
 * @return {number}
 */
var myPow = function(x, n) {
    if (n < 0) {
        x = 1 / x;
        n = -n;
    }
    return pow(x, n);

    function pow(x, n) {
        if (n == 0) {
            return 1.0;
        }
        const half = pow(x, parseInt(n / 2));
        if (n % 2 === 0) {
            return half * half;
        } else {
            return half * half * x;
        }
    }
};
```

