## **Approach:
***1] Create a string of all the operators. Create a stack list.
2] Check the each single item from the given String[] tokens for whether it is an operator or not.
3] If it is not an operator, simply push it in the stack. and go for the next item.
4} If it is an operator, pop out the first two elements of the stack.
5] Check the type of operator, and return the respective expression. [ like op1  op2, etc*]*****

***CODE:***

