![image](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/8acc63ff-b1ee-4a09-8a1f-9fb5883ef43f_1606751823.8832223.png)


Since they are not equal we will have to move one of the pointers, top or bottom. We will move the bottom pointer. The reason we are moving the bottom pointer is `bottom[0] < top[0]`, and this works because both the arrays are sorted.
![image](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/4b78c1c4-f191-427a-8d4a-e2b6b79817a1_1606750256.1911736.png)

Since `top[0] = bottom[1]` we can add the item to the end array. Now we have to incrament the top counter and bottom counter by one.
![image](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/69b578d7-c8df-4214-b909-ab4e756131c5_1606750591.901871.png)

`top[1] != bottom[2]` and `top[1] < bottom[2]` so we add one to the top counter.
![image](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/3b79be0c-60d2-4e2f-a61b-c20a47232131_1606750855.6892686.png)

`top[2] = bottom[2]` so we add the item, `4` to the end array. To end this part we add one to the top counter and bottom counter.
![image](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/2704966c-083e-464a-a0b5-b4c414bcb86c_1606751064.5167634.png)

`top[3] != bottom[3]` and `top[3] > bottom[3]` so we add one to the bottom counter.
![image](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/8505773a-54e3-4ccb-99f9-0b0f61658071_1606751215.7158778.png)

`top[3] = bottom[4]` so we add the item to the end array. Now we add one to each counter, bottom and top.
![image](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/31fb6b6c-c49b-4dbc-bf5c-a61555686a7e_1606751363.7848818.png)

`top[4] != bottom[5]` and `top[4] < bottom[5]` so we add one to the top counter.
![image](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/b3b0bd9d-cad1-4bcb-852f-b5f0a25a22c6_1606751516.2833507.png)

`top[5] = bottom[5]` so we add the item, `7` to the end array. Now we add one to the top and bottom counter.
![image](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/925f8f4a-8496-4bf3-ae55-254f06601a6e_1606751644.8628895.png)

But now the only problem is on the top counter we have run out of items, because of this we break out of the loop and return the value.

